      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model with bilinear isotropic hardening for post-yield regime. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) between screw-rod interface. Model form is consistent with the physics of quasi-static ASTM F1717 compression-bending and has been used in published FDA validation studies for similar constructs."
