      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and Poisson ratio (0.34) sourced from 2023 coupon tensile testing dataset. Screw geometry parameterized from CMM measurements of three production-lot screws. Input uncertainty propagated via one-at-a-time sensitivity analysis; QoI sensitivity to material inputs is low (<3% variation across ±2-sigma material property range)."
