      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production-representative hardware tested across two independent laboratories. Sample size sufficient to characterize experimental variability (CV < 5% for all QoIs). Samples confirmed to be from production-representative lots per device history records."
