      "acceptanceCriteria": "Multiple test conditions (load levels, fixation configurations) required to achieve Level 2; only single ASTM F1717 standard configuration tested.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single standard ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration at a single load rate. Only one fixation block spacing (44 mm) was evaluated. Variation in test conditions (e.g., load rate, block spacing) was not explored. Achieved level (1) is below the required level (2) for this factor; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the regulatory precedent for this test method."
    },
