      "rationale": "Three QoIs compared: construct stiffness (4.7% difference, E/uval=0.91), yield force (6.2%, E/uval=1.14), force at 40 mm (8.1%, E/uval=1.52). All QoIs satisfy pre-specified bounds of <10% difference and E/uval < 1.96. Experimental uncertainty estimated from inter-laboratory and inter-specimen variability using GUM methodology."
    },
